{"an8.37:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 8.37 ","an8.37:0.2":"4. Danavagga ","an8.37:0.3":"Sappurisadanasutta ","an8.37:1.1":"“Atthimani, bhikkhave, sappurisadanani. ","an8.37:1.2":"Katamani attha? ","an8.37:1.3":"Sucim deti, panitam deti, kalena deti, kappiyam deti, viceyya deti, abhinham deti, dadam cittam pasadeti, datva attamano hoti. ","an8.37:1.4":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, attha sappurisadananiti. ","an8.37:2.1":"Sucim panitam kalena, ","an8.37:2.2":"kappiyam panabhojanam; ","an8.37:2.3":"Abhinham dadati danam, ","an8.37:2.4":"sukhettesu brahmacarisu. ","an8.37:3.1":"Neva vippatisarissa, ","an8.37:3.2":"cajitva amisam bahum; ","an8.37:3.3":"Evam dinnani danani, ","an8.37:3.4":"vannayanti vipassino. ","an8.37:4.1":"Evam yajitva medhavi, ","an8.37:4.2":"saddho muttena cetasa; ","an8.37:4.3":"Abyabajjham sukham lokam, ","an8.37:4.4":"pandito upapajjati”ti. ","an8.37:4.5":"Sattamam. "}